        </div>
        <div class="card-info">
          <h2 class="card-title">Modern SaaS / Creative</h2>
          <p class="card-description">Sleek, dark mode with vibrant gradients and modern UI elements</p>
          <span class="card-tag modern-tag">SaaS</span>
